# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We pledge to make participation in our project a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Our Standards
Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment include being respectful and constructive.

## Enforcement Responsibilities
Project maintainers are responsible for clarifying and enforcing standards.

## Scope
This Code of Conduct applies within all project spaces.

## Enforcement
Instances of abusive behavior may be reported and will be reviewed.

## Enforcement Guidelines
Maintainers will take appropriate actions in response to violations.

## Attribution
This Code of Conduct is adapted from common open-source community guidelines.
